<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <style>
    .hero {
      background-image: 
  linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0),#D7DAE5,#D7DAE5, #D7DAE5), 
  url(/images/imagery/DSC_0081.JPG);
  
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .bio img, .owner img {
      width: 50%;
      height: auto;
      /* margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px; */
    }

    .bio, .owner, .custom-work, .wood-types, .stain-colors {
      padding: 0 8vw 0 8vw; 
    }

    .bio, .owner {
      border-radius: 25px 0 0 25px;
    }

    /* Flexbox for desktop view (left-right) */
    .section {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center; /* Vertically center content */
      justify-content: space-between; /* Space out title and content */
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .section .text {
      flex: 1;
      padding-right: 20px; /* Add some space between text and image */
    }

    .section img {
      flex: 0 0 40%; /* Image takes up 40% of the width */
      max-width: 100%; /* Ensure image scales properly */
    }
    .customImg {
  display: flex; /* Use Flexbox for layout */
  justify-content: space-between; /* Add space between the images */
  align-items: center; /* Vertically align the images */
  gap: 10px; /* Add spacing between images */
  padding-bottom:40px;
}

.customImg img {
  flex: 1; /* Allow images to grow and shrink equally */
  max-width: 25%; /* Ensure each image takes up a maximum of 30% of the container */
  max-height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
}

    /* Mobile view (title, image, text stacked vertically) */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .section {
        flex-direction: column; /* Stack elements vertically */
        align-items: center; /* Center content */
        text-align: center; /* Center text */
      }

      .section img {
        width: 80%; /* Image takes up 80% width on mobile */
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .section .text {
        padding-right: 0; /* Remove extra padding on smaller screens */
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="hero">
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <div class="highlight">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="bio section" style="margin-top:40px;">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
        <p>Pundsack Cabinets has been creating high-quality custom cabinetry for over a decade. Our shop is dedicated to providing top-notch craftsmanship and personalized service for every project we undertake.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="/images/imagery/shop-photo.jpg" alt="Our Shop">
    </div>

    <div class="owner section">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="section-title">Meet the Owner</h2>
        <p>With years of experience and a deep love for woodworking, Greg Pundsack brings both skill and vision to every project.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="/images/imagery/headshot.JPG" alt="Owner Headshot">
    </div>

    <div class="custom-work section" style="padding: 0 50px 0 50px;width: 80%; margin: auto;">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="section-title">Custom Work</h2>
        <p>At Pundsack Cabinets, we pride ourselves on being able to create anything you envision. From custom cabinetry to unique pieces, we can build one-of-a-kind items tailored to your specific needs. Whether itâ€™s a bold design or a simple piece, if you can dream it, we can craft it.</p>
        <div class="customImg">
        <img src="/images/imagery/IMG_2676.jpeg"> <img src="/images/imagery/IMG_3237.jpeg"> <img src="/images/imagery/IMG_3654.jpeg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wood-types section">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="section-title">Wood Types</h2>
        <p>We work with a variety of wood types to bring your vision to life.</p>
        <a href="/wood"><button>Learn More</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stain-colors section">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="section-title">Finishes</h2>
        <p>Learn more about the variety of finishes we offer.</p>
        <a href="/stain"><button>Stains</button></a>
        <a href="/paint"><button>Painted</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>  

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
